title: Tired
itunes:title: Tired
description:
Good morning everyone. I've been married to my husband for eight years have three kids. Last year two deer rammed into the side of my car and totaled it out. So I've had to use his car for work. If I have to go anywhere else I have to fight with him just to get the car and I'm tired of fussing with him. He doesn't go anywhere.
